description:
We are the #7th collection on BRC-721. Our world is called the "7th Universe".
There are 1458 PEPEs permanently engraved on the Bitcoin blockchain. Our physical bodies will gradually be eroded by the passage of time until they disappear. But PEPEs will exist forever, until the end of the world. We hope that the spirit of PEPE can be perpetuated just like these inscriptions
name: BRC721 PEPE
